579
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:36,410
A spoon rest?

580
00:37:36,410 --> 00:37:38,540
One second. I have to take this.

581
00:37:41,300 --> 00:37:43,400
Hello.

582
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,720
