00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,480
Want some coffee?

586
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:58,040
No.

587
00:37:58,040 --> 00:38:00,560
Get back to work. I'll get going.

588
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:05,200
You know...

589
00:38:07,130 --> 00:38:10,250
when is your doctor's appointment?

590
00:38:13,640 --> 00:38:16,710
Want me to come with you?

591
00:38:16,710 --> 00:38:18,810
