598
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:46,700
Then, remember the restaurant I said I liked?

599
00:38:46,700 --> 00:38:48,600
When I used to load packages?

600
00:38:48,600 --> 00:38:50,100
Sounds good.

601
00:38:51,600 --> 00:38:53,220
