602
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:55,440
Bye.

603
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:59,600
Don't go.

604
00:39:05,740 --> 00:39:08,100
- Hello!
- Hello.

605
00:39:08,100 --> 00:39:10,320
Are you the only one here, Gi Bbeum?

606
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:13,900
They're smoking. Have a seat.

607
00:39:15,930 --> 00:39:17,350
Hey.

608
00:39:17,350 --> 00:39:19,590
You look great!

609
00:39:19,590 --> 00:39:23,590
Really? I guess I'm kind of happy these days.

610
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:28,390
Why are you happy? I have an idea.

611
00:39:28,390 --> 00:39:30,450
Come on.

