655
00:41:43,890 --> 00:41:46,210
- So good.
- Geez.

656
00:41:49,810 --> 00:41:52,150
Do you think I could work
in the entertainment industry?

657
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:53,580
You?

658
00:41:53,580 --> 00:41:55,740
Don't even go there.

659
00:42:00,250 --> 00:42:03,050
What? Are you serious?

660
00:42:05,130 --> 00:42:08,310
If you're asking seriously...

661
00:42:08,310 --> 00:42:10,080
Don't.

662
00:42:10,080 --> 00:42:12,740
I know nothing is easy in this world,

663
00:42:12,740 --> 00:42:16,050
