667
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:41,710
Take back one move.

668
00:42:41,710 --> 00:42:43,740
That won't cut it.

669
00:42:43,740 --> 00:42:45,580
How many moves, exactly?

670
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:47,940
Hyung, I'm here!

671
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,800
Teacher! What are you doing here?

672
00:42:50,800 --> 00:42:53,650
I wanted to eat Geon No's food.

673
00:42:53,650 --> 00:42:56,200
I don't know when I'll get to.

674
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:59,200
- I'm going to Australia.
- Australia?

675
00:43:00,590 --> 00:43:02,330
- What?
- Whatever!

676
00:43:02,330 --> 00:43:04,400
I already booked my ticket.
Don't talk me out of it.

677
00:43:04,400 --> 00:43:05,750
Goodbye, Korea!

678
00:43:05,750 --> 00:43:09,200
Wait, y-you were serious about going?

679
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:11,730
- Huh?
- Teacher, don't go!

680
00:43:11,730 --> 00:43:13,800
Don't go!

681
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:16,770
Oops. I spilled everything.

682
00:43:16,770 --> 00:43:19,570
Geon No, what is wrong with you?

683
00:43:19,570 --> 00:43:21,760
It's not like we see each other that often.

684
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:23,650
You came to drink makgeolli a few times.

685
00:43:23,650 --> 00:43:25,180
I was proud and happy about it.

686
00:43:25,180 --> 00:43:27,650
That's right. Just drink the makgeolli. Don't leave.

687
00:43:27,650 --> 00:43:30,100
You can't even speak English!

688
00:43:30,100 --> 00:43:32,840
Hey. Do you want the bookstore?

689
00:43:32,840 --> 00:43:35,180
Go clean it up every once in a while.

690
00:43:35,180 --> 00:43:37,800
I want to keep it since it was
my grandmother's dying wish.

691
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:39,350
No!

692
00:43:40,170 --> 00:43:43,840
Gosh, that guy. Are you mad? Hey!

693
00:43:43,840 --> 00:43:46,000
 You guys can come and visit Australia! 

694
00:43:46,000 --> 00:43:48,740
 I'll become a surf master and wait for you! 

695
00:43:49,700 --> 00:43:51,160
 - Geon No.
- Yes? 

696
00:43:51,160 --> 00:43:52,710
 You spilled on purpose, didn't you? 

697
00:43:52,710 --> 00:43:54,450
 Let's start over. 

698
00:43:56,650 --> 00:43:57,860
Teacher!

699
00:43:57,860 --> 00:43:59,190
Huh?

700
00:43:59,190 --> 00:44:01,410
Can you make it alone?

701
00:44:01,410 --> 00:44:03,840
You had way too much makgeolli.

702
00:44:03,840 --> 00:44:06,010
You reek.

703
00:44:06,010 --> 00:44:07,400
Let's go. I'll take you.

704
00:44:07,400 --> 00:44:11,310
Gosh, come on! No! I'm so close.

705
00:44:11,310 --> 00:44:13,340
Hey.

706
00:44:13,340 --> 00:44:14,500
 

