00:44:31,650 --> 00:44:35,110
It's too far.

711
00:44:35,110 --> 00:44:37,440
We can video chat.

712
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:41,160
Stop being so cheesy.

713
00:44:42,390 --> 00:44:43,890
I'm leaving.

