00:45:45,650 --> 00:45:49,150
Hey, Seok Joo.

730
00:45:50,200 --> 00:45:51,570
Hey.

731
00:45:52,760 --> 00:45:55,470
I thought it would be better to

732
00:45:55,470 --> 00:45:58,980
hear it from a doctor than me trying to explain it.

