00:45:58,980 --> 00:46:00,320
Did that scare you?

734
00:46:00,320 --> 00:46:02,170
Of course it did.

735
00:46:03,330 --> 00:46:05,020
Does Nu Ri know that you're sick?

736
00:46:05,020 --> 00:46:06,910
