00:46:14,160 --> 00:46:18,520
I've just known this day would come someday.

740
00:46:18,520 --> 00:46:20,920
Just...

741
00:46:20,920 --> 00:46:23,180
don't be too shocked if something happens.

742
00:46:23,180 --> 00:46:25,420
Just because I know doesn't
mean I won't be shocked.

743
00:46:25,420 --> 00:46:28,680
I'm just scared in advance. How could you-

