00:46:30,830 --> 00:46:33,560
Do you know why I liked you, Hyung?

745
00:46:33,560 --> 00:46:37,850
Because you make my life more complicated.

746
00:46:37,850 --> 00:46:41,420
Because you accept me as I am.

747
00:46:42,590 --> 00:46:44,030
But...

