00:52:17,300 --> 00:52:19,030
relieved.

808
00:52:21,200 --> 00:52:22,560
Yeah.

809
00:52:23,430 --> 00:52:25,830
I think so.

810
00:52:25,830 --> 00:52:30,900
Of course, I don't know what's at the end
